text: Hiroshi Nosaka (1 October 1914 - 19 August 2004) was a Japanese gymnast. He competed in eight events at the 1936 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1914 births Category:2004 deaths Category:Japanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1936 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
